OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780049133
OL,3,CBoy, 14, dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty in river
OL,6,FA teenage boy has died in Oxford after
OL,7,Fgetting into difficulty in the River
OL,8,FThames.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Thames Valley Police
OL,11,Fsaid: "We are sad to confirm a boy
OL,12,Fdied after getting into difficulty in
OL,13,Fthe River Thames at Donnington Bridge
OL,14,Fyesterday.
OL,16,F"The 14-year-old boy's family have
OL,17,Fbeen informed and offered support; our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with them at this
OL,19,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
