OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780049133
OL,3,CBoy, 14, dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty in river
OL,6,F"The death is being treated as
OL,7,Funexplained but not suspicious and our
OL,8,Finvestigation is ongoing."
OL,10,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,11,Fat Donnington Bridge, in Oxford, at
OL,12,F5.45pm on Wednesday, following reports
OL,13,Fof a person in difficulty in the water.
OL,15,FThe bridge was temporarily closed
OL,16,Fwhile emergency services responded.
OL,18,FThe teenager is the eleventh person to
OL,19,Fdie across the UK during the heatwave,
OL,20,Fafter getting into difficulty in the
OL,21,Fwater.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
